tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"lunch茶記有電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ff4581ede5bbc9cd01d261410394bee071694e","tid":769303,"uid":67867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T23:30:02.000Z","msg":"你老母隻腳仲正"},{"pid":"b08da255a56e4cf684474882bd5b2cf98e5f3d1b","tid":769303,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T13:25:01.000Z","msg":"轉貼自11年前嘅鄉土<br />\n<br />\n宋熙年 既食相似餓鬼托世 真係好核突 日日有食神 有相<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位有冇睇&lt;&lt;日日有食神&gt;&gt;....<br />\n我真係睇到火都滾...<br />\n見到個宋熙年...佢既食相真係...好樣衰呀!        下面有相!!<br />\n仲要話比人聽佢係華姐冠軍...<br />\n食野食到&quot;JAP JAP&quot; 聲唔在講,<br />\n有冇留意佢一食野,<br />\n擘到個口勁大,之後唔知做乜要伸條利出黎先塞D野入口,<br />\n食到面容X曲...<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢講野好假...用詞永遠都係得&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;哇!!!正&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<br />\n次次稻稻同佢講,&quot;&quot;下次我同你去食XXXX呀&quot;&quot;......佢永遠都係答&quot;&quot;&quot;哇!!!XXXX,正&quot;&quot;&quot;!!!<br />\n<br />\n我頂呀,睇見呢隻野真係胃都反晒....日日有食神...睇到佢都飽,食乜鬼!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpikyOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpikyOX.png&h=6016b117&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQ12M8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQ12M8Z.png&h=ff9bd460&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbiHM81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpbiHM81.png&h=c259739c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxhmifJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxhmifJ.png&h=4d3e7926&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DvSNdO5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDvSNdO5.png&h=b1f6e8a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNU0yO7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNU0yO7.png&h=b84cff16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7S9r88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7S9r88.png&h=c412446c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nhttp://mytv.&gt;&gt;&gt;&lt;&lt;&lt;.com<br />\n<br />\n大家可以去呢條LINK到睇返,日日有食神既重溫,重溫一下呢位,餓鬼托世十年冇食過野既.........餓鬼!"}]}